connect20/techinflo_productlookbook.name: connect20/Techinflo_Productlookbook

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/techinflo_productlookbook.description: This extension allows a vendor to upload Images with the popular styles /trend and then customer can click on a particular part of the image, like Dress, Accessories, footwear etc, to view the matching products.
